---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="nubui Icon System Test">
  <h1>nubui Icon System Test</h1>

  <section>
    <h2>Generated Icon Classes</h2>
    <p>nubui generates Tailwind CSS classes for SVG icons. Use the <code>mask-icon-{name}</code> class to display icons.</p>

    <h3>Basic Icon Usage</h3>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
      <span class="mask-icon-heart w-6 h-6 text-red-500 inline-block"></span>
      <span class="mask-icon-star w-6 h-6 text-yellow-500 inline-block"></span>
      <span class="mask-icon-heart w-8 h-8 text-blue-500 inline-block"></span>
    </div>

    <h3>Icon Color Variations</h3>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
      <span class="mask-icon-star w-6 h-6 text-gray-400 inline-block"></span>
      <span class="mask-icon-star w-6 h-6 text-gray-600 inline-block"></span>
      <span class="mask-icon-star w-6 h-6 text-gray-800 inline-block"></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Icon Component Pattern</h2>
    <p>Create reusable icon components for your framework:</p>

    <h3>Example Icon Component Usage</h3>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
      <span class="mask-icon-heart w-6 h-6 text-red-500 inline-block" aria-label="Heart icon"></span>
      <span class="mask-icon-star w-6 h-6 text-yellow-500 inline-block" aria-label="Star icon"></span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Button with Icon Pattern</h2>
    <p>Build buttons that include icons using the generated classes:</p>

    <button style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background-color: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 0.375rem; border: none; cursor: pointer;">
      <span class="mask-icon-heart w-4 h-4 inline-block"></span>
      Like
    </button>

    <button style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background-color: #dc2626; color: white; border-radius: 0.375rem; border: none; cursor: pointer; margin-left: 0.5rem;">
      <span class="mask-icon-star w-4 h-4 inline-block"></span>
      Favorite
    </button>
  </section>
</Layout>
